							您现在的位置：&nbsp;<a class="LinkPath" href="http://www.tgbus.com">电玩巴士</a>&nbsp;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;<a class="LinkPath" href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/Index.shtml">PS4</a>&nbsp;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;<a class="LinkPath" href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/Index.shtml">资讯中心</a>&nbsp;&gt;&gt;&nbsp;正文
