					<div id="body" class="article">
						<div class="art-title">
							<h3 class="mt2">《如龙极》图文流程攻略(13)</h3>
							<p>
								<span class="ptag">编辑：建安余韵  </span>
								<span class="ptag">来源：TGBUS原创</span>
								<span class="ptag">发布时间：2016/1/22 19:46:08 </span>
								<span class="ptag">热度：<script type="text/javascript"> document.write('<script src=\"http://tracker.tgbus.com/count/?type=' + STYPE + '&id=' + IDENTIFY + '&show=1\">' + '</' + 'script>');</script><script src="http://tracker.tgbus.com/count/?type=tvgame&amp;id=471828&amp;show=1"></script>111473</span>
								<a href="http://bbs.tgbus.com/forum-9-1.html" class="file" target="_blank">我要爆料</a>
							</p>
							<div id="headdh" class="art-box" style="padding-top: 10px;"><div class="pindex"><ul class="cl"><li> <span class="num">1</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608.shtml">第 1 页：系统说明</a></li><li> <span class="num">2</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_2.shtml">第 2 页：第一章</a></li><li> <span class="num">3</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_3.shtml">第 3 页：第二章</a></li><li> <span class="num">4</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_4.shtml">第 4 页：第三章</a></li><li> <span class="num">5</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_5.shtml">第 5 页：第四章</a></li><li> <span class="num">6</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_6.shtml">第 6 页：第五章</a></li><li> <span class="num">7</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_7.shtml">第 7 页：第六章</a></li><li> <span class="num">8</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_8.shtml">第 8 页：第七章</a></li><li> <span class="num">9</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_9.shtml">第 9 页：第八章</a></li><li> <span class="num">10</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_10.shtml">第 10 页：第九章</a></li><li> <span class="num">11</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_11.shtml">第 11 页：第十章</a></li><li> <span class="num">12</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_12.shtml">第 12 页：第十一章</a></li><li> <span class="num">13</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_13.shtml"><font color="red">第 13 页：第十二章</font></a></li><li> <span class="num">14</span><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_14.shtml">第 14 页：第十三章</a></li></ul></div></div>
			
						</div>
						<div id="body" class="art-box">
							<div class="art-intro mt2 pt2 txt">
								<p>
									《如龙：极》已于1月21日正式上市，电玩巴士第一时间为各位玩家带来本作的图文和视频攻略，目前资料持续更新中。
								</p>
							</div>
							<p></p>
<p>　　<strong><font color="#0000ff">第十二章　重逢</font></strong></p>
<p align="center"><a style="WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201601/20160123172659848.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://tv01.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/OTEzRCw1ODAsMTAwLDQsMywxLC0xLDAscms1MCw2MS4xNTIuMjQyLjE=/u/ps4.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201601/20160123172659832.jpg"></a></p>
<p>　　开始可以和移动武器商那买一点血药或者装备。之后来到船上看到寺田，他表示自己也是受到风间很多恩情因此也打算帮助我们。之后风间把关于美月的真相都告诉了桐生和遥。之后嶋野组过来叫嚣我们准备迎战。</p>
<p align="center"><a style="WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201601/20160123172659746.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://tv02.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/QTdERSw1ODAsMTAwLDQsMywxLC0xLDAscms1MCw2MS4xNTIuMjQyLjE=/u/ps4.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201601/20160123172659541.jpg"></a></p>
<p><font color="#0000ff">　　战斗：嶋野组成员</font></p>
<p>　　对付嶋野组成员可以选择火爆浪子+各种武器的方式，其中有个武田使用电锯非常烦人，很容易打断进攻的节奏，而且血超厚，船上空间也毕竟狭小。然后还要注意其中有一个衫山在远处放冷枪，优先拿到他的散弹枪会比较有优势。</p>
<p align="center"><a style="WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201601/20160123172659669.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://tv03.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/NjIwRiw1ODAsMTAwLDQsMywxLC0xLDAscms1MCw2MS4xNTIuMjQyLjE=/u/ps4.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201601/20160123172700352.jpg"></a></p>
<p><font color="#0000ff">　　战斗：嶋野太</font></p>
<p>　　这次的嶋野太其实比一开始我们没什么技能的时候好对付多了，由于是周围还有很多成员的混战，BOSS偶尔也会和他们纠缠在一起，给我们很好的进攻机会。个人是一遍和这些杂兵战斗一边和BOSS打，用火爆浪子可以大范围削减杂兵的血。</p>
<p>　　嶋野太还是老样子非常喜欢揪着人，我们要快速连打X键挣脱。当然由于BOSS进攻非常缓慢而且破绽很大，切换成快攻手风格也非常有优势，当然注意对付他进入状态时候快速切回火爆浪子来发动超级精髓。场景远处还有一些血药和摩托车之类的道具可以利用。</p>
<p align="center"><a style="WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201601/20160123172700256.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://tv04.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/NjNFQyw1ODAsMTAwLDQsMywxLC0xLDAscms1MCw2MS4xNTIuMjQyLjE=/u/ps4.tgbus.com/UploadFiles/201601/20160123172700871.jpg"></a></p>
<p>　　战斗之后风间把世良胜的遗言拿给了桐生。</p>
<p></p><p align="center" class="contentpager" count="14"><b><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_8.shtml">&nbsp;&lt;&lt;&nbsp;</a><a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_12.shtml">上一页</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_9.shtml">[9]</a>&nbsp;<a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_10.shtml">[10]</a>&nbsp;<a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_11.shtml">[11]</a>&nbsp;<a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_12.shtml">[12]</a>&nbsp;<font color="red">[13]</font>&nbsp;<a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_14.shtml">[14]</a>&nbsp;<a href="http://ps4.tgbus.com/news/201601/20160122194608_14.shtml">下一页</a> </b></p>
